## Tim Griesser

Creator of [Bookshelf.js](http://bookshelfjs.org), [Knex.js](http://knexjs.org); frequent contributor
to [Backbone.js](http://backbonejs.org) and other open source projects and libraries.

### About

Should be getting more of a real site here sometime soon, in the meantime checkout one of my projects listed above and feel free to open a ticket if you see anything you'd like changed!

### Contact

You can find me [@tgriesser](http://twitter.com/tgriesser) or via email: tgriesser at gmail dot com.
